Package de.ikor.sip.foundation.core.declarative.orchestration.common.dsl

Interface StepResultCloner<T>

Type Parameters:
T - Type of the element to be cloned
All Superinterfaces:
Function<T,T>
Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface public interface StepResultCloner<T> extends Function<T,T>
Interface for cloning a step-result (response) during an orchestration process.

Default implementations for common use-cases are provided via forCloneable(), forSerializable(), and forCopyConstructor().
